WEBVTT

00:00:06.966 --> 00:00:11.388
What have I done for God? Sidney, Australia, 19920211

00:00:11.684 --> 00:00:14.178
Very good idea to have a good lounge.

00:00:14.379 --> 00:00:18.926
I wish they have it in every airport.

00:00:23.026 --> 00:00:27.537
But they, in India they don't even allow Me inside the airport

00:00:27.738 --> 00:00:33.128
It's difficult.

00:00:48.040 --> 00:00:51.418
In Perth, we had this Ganesha Puja,

00:00:51.618 --> 00:00:56.180
and I really spoke very nicely on equilibrium.

00:00:56.381 --> 00:01:02.237
And the rain, expressed its equilibrium,

00:01:02.437 --> 00:01:07.439
but when they were singing, it was very quiet.

00:01:07.640 --> 00:01:09.883
And when it stopped for a short time suddenly it came

00:01:10.083 --> 00:01:14.121
with a complete gusto and sang some songs and went away again.

00:01:14.322 --> 00:01:18.317
Just for the aarti to start with. It’s very beautiful it was.

00:01:18.518 --> 00:01:20.588
So dramatic.

00:01:20.789 --> 00:01:24.635
Is very interesting.

00:01:34.451 --> 00:01:38.100
So all preparations are done for the puja?

00:01:38.301 --> 00:01:44.200
Maybe some people might come up from abroad, I don’t know, maybe.

00:01:46.171 --> 00:01:49.780
Have you written to some leaders or not?

00:01:49.981 --> 00:01:52.024
About this puja that we are going to have?

00:01:52.224 --> 00:01:54.149
Yogi: I think yes some invitations were sent out.

00:01:54.349 --> 00:01:56.445
Shri Mataji: Might have gone out.

00:01:56.645 --> 00:01:59.422
Yogi: There are one or two people coming.

00:01:59.622 --> 00:02:01.531
Shri Mataji: They might come. Yogi: Only individuals.

00:02:01.731 --> 00:02:04.399
I invited a few people at Ganapatipule and they said;

00:02:04.599 --> 00:02:07.560
‘Oh, it’s such a long way.’ And I said: ‘But you always expect us

00:02:07.760 --> 00:02:11.115
to come to yours. Shri Mataji: Yes.

00:02:11.315 --> 00:02:15.705
They have to move.

00:02:18.582 --> 00:02:23.240
Columbus could go to America, why not you people go to Australia?

00:02:23.440 --> 00:02:27.268
Can’t understand.

00:02:30.718 --> 00:02:32.213
Yogi: And a much more comfortable trip.

00:02:32.413 --> 00:02:34.920
Shri Mataji: Yes, much more comfortable. They found

00:02:35.121 --> 00:02:39.155
a much more comfortable place to live in.

00:02:39.356 --> 00:02:43.883
He was really lost. But in a way thank God, you see?

00:02:44.083 --> 00:02:47.086
Otherwise there would have been no Indian left in India,

00:02:47.286 --> 00:02:51.325
if he had come here by chance.

00:03:12.206 --> 00:03:15.904
Come forward, come forward, you come forward here.

00:03:16.104 --> 00:03:20.072
Yes, good.

00:03:50.758 --> 00:03:55.266
So many flowers, beautiful.

00:04:04.668 --> 00:04:08.425
[Marathi/Hindi]

00:04:34.568 --> 00:04:40.544
The children can come here in front, come along.

00:04:54.640 --> 00:04:58.765
How many of you are suffering from hepatitis?

00:05:03.324 --> 00:05:07.816
Can you come this side? Who else?

00:05:10.955 --> 00:05:15.110
Only one?

00:05:16.252 --> 00:05:20.884
They told Me ten are suffering.

00:06:35.002 --> 00:06:40.917
In Singapore I bought a book, very interesting,

00:06:41.117 --> 00:06:44.860
called as: ‘Faces of Islam.’

00:06:45.061 --> 00:06:49.921
And I was surprised that the whole concept of Islam is Sahaja.

00:06:50.121 --> 00:06:52.835
Absolutely.

00:06:53.036 --> 00:06:59.404
And all the, authors and all the people,

00:06:59.604 --> 00:07:05.344
who have discussed there, are saying that Muslims are not Islamic.

00:07:05.545 --> 00:07:10.344
They don’t follow Islam. That’s why
their whole thing has become so rigid.

00:07:10.545 --> 00:07:14.566
I mean so surprising that book has revealed to Me the confessions,

00:07:14.766 --> 00:07:22.225
of these people. And the society that Mohammed Sahib has talked about is ours.

00:07:22.426 --> 00:07:25.636
Muslims are nowhere. Absolutely the way He has described

00:07:25.837 --> 00:07:31.595
how the brotherhood would be there, how righteousness would be there.

00:07:31.796 --> 00:07:34.793
But one thing is missing I feel, that He said:

00:07:34.993 --> 00:07:38.551
"You must seek the knowledge. You must seek the Truth."

00:07:38.752 --> 00:07:42.037
Despite that, whatever was Islam, they are free to seek

00:07:42.238 --> 00:07:46.153
the knowledge and to learn from others. Can you imagine?

00:07:46.354 --> 00:07:49.651
And He has said how to deal with non-Muslims also.

00:07:49.852 --> 00:07:53.432
And they said that there are many who are just minimal Muslims.

00:07:53.632 --> 00:07:56.449
Some of them are just for name’s sake, they are not Muslims.

00:07:56.650 --> 00:08:00.371
I mean I was so amazed. We have such a misunderstanding,

00:08:00.572 --> 00:08:05.468
that I always said that all these Incarnations and Prophets,

00:08:05.669 --> 00:08:11.561
came to establish a religion which was really Sahaja Yoga.

00:08:11.762 --> 00:08:14.722
All their expectations were Sahaja Yoga.

00:08:14.922 --> 00:08:18.257
And they have deviated so much,

00:08:18.457 --> 00:08:22.564
that you start wondering what is this, as in Christianity, you see.

00:08:22.765 --> 00:08:27.280
How much it has deviated, Christianity, to what level it has gone,

00:08:27.480 --> 00:08:30.351
it is shocking, really shocking.

00:08:30.552 --> 00:08:35.151
I don’t know if you know of a book written ‘In God’s Name’.

00:08:35.352 --> 00:08:41.077
And in that book, it reads like a novel actually,

00:08:41.277 --> 00:08:47.320
I mean it’s very interesting. In that
book the writer has suggested that

00:08:47.520 --> 00:08:52.061
this present pope is responsible for the murder of the previous one.

00:08:52.262 --> 00:08:56.245
And there were thirteen or fourteen murders took place,

00:08:56.445 --> 00:08:59.990
just to hide this. Can you beat it?

00:09:00.191 --> 00:09:04.651
And recently one of the persons was murdered was Calvi.

00:09:04.852 --> 00:09:09.097
And they say, that this Calvi was murdered,

00:09:09.298 --> 00:09:12.904
It was - I mean every week in Italy since I am there,

00:09:13.105 --> 00:09:16.958
some new exposures are coming. But this Calvi was murdered

00:09:17.159 --> 00:09:22.951
in a way that he was hanged on one of the bridges of London.

00:09:23.152 --> 00:09:30.078
And if he was, he was the one, the one who murdered him,

00:09:30.278 --> 00:09:36.046
he said that: "I am a member of mafia, all right,

00:09:36.246 --> 00:09:39.635
but I was paid by this Vatican, by this pope,

00:09:39.836 --> 00:09:43.771
for murdering that man." Is a confession from him.

00:09:43.972 --> 00:09:48.331
And Mr Heard was questioned:

00:09:48.531 --> 00:09:50.859
"Why didn’t you take action against this when these things

00:09:51.060 --> 00:09:54.343
happen in England?" He says: ‘What’s the use? Because they would kill

00:09:54.544 --> 00:09:58.935
all our lawyers, our judges, everyone. It’s all mafia."

00:09:59.136 --> 00:10:04.458
So the whole system of Catholic Church is nothing but mafia.

00:10:04.659 --> 00:10:13.569
Nine million dollars of counterfeit were printed and were distributed

00:10:13.769 --> 00:10:20.131
through their bank, that is Vatican Bank. Can you believe it?

00:10:20.332 --> 00:10:26.091
I mean this is Christianity. Is this what Christ preached?

00:10:26.292 --> 00:10:28.705
Killing people, doing all kinds of things.

00:10:28.906 --> 00:10:32.884
I mean nowhere I find Mohammed decrying anyone. He said:

00:10:33.085 --> 00:10:36.564
"You have to believe in everyone". Only these people are saying,

00:10:36.765 --> 00:10:39.603
that He was the last.

00:10:39.804 --> 00:10:44.376
He went to this limit to say that: "I am not Divine.

00:10:44.577 --> 00:10:47.267
I follow the Divine laws but I am not Divine."

00:10:47.468 --> 00:10:52.757
May be just He wanted people to follow.

00:10:52.958 --> 00:10:56.049
Surprising I was really surprised that

00:10:56.249 --> 00:11:00.422
if Koran is teaching such great things,

00:11:00.623 --> 00:11:05.016
the Muslims are just on the other side of it and they admit

00:11:05.216 --> 00:11:11.651
that Islam should not be confused with Muslims.

00:11:13.182 --> 00:11:16.790
In the same way we can say that Christianity should not be

00:11:16.990 --> 00:11:21.422
confused with Christians. What about Judaism?

00:11:21.622 --> 00:11:25.475
Same thing. I mean nowhere in that religion

00:11:25.675 --> 00:11:29.091
taught to be like this, the way they are behaving.

00:11:29.292 --> 00:11:33.277
They are following Hitler, out and out. The one who killed them,

00:11:33.478 --> 00:11:37.871
tortured them, they are becoming just like them.

00:11:38.071 --> 00:11:42.047
So what to say about these human beings as under the name of God,

00:11:42.247 --> 00:11:45.609
under the name of religion, behaving like this?

00:11:45.810 --> 00:11:48.536
The reason they have given many: "Because of this and because of that."

00:11:48.737 --> 00:11:51.701
Just a minute, will you pleas keep quiet?

00:11:51.901 --> 00:11:54.739
You must bahave. You are Sahaja Yogis, aren't you?

00:11:54.940 --> 00:11:58.340
You are Sahaja Yogis or not? Sahaja Yogis don't bekave like that.

00:11:58.541 --> 00:12:02.961
See how nicely they are all sitting.

00:12:04.563 --> 00:12:12.365
So, this aspect that they are saying that:

00:12:12.565 --> 00:12:15.967
"Because the people didn’t read Koran properly,

00:12:16.168 --> 00:12:19.640
they didn’t understand properly, they should have been educated properly."

00:12:19.840 --> 00:12:25.344
It will take thousand years to educate every Muslim about it.

00:12:36.959 --> 00:12:42.038
And if they think that by teaching through their Book,

00:12:42.238 --> 00:12:45.339
it will be imbibed, it’s not possible.

00:12:45.540 --> 00:12:48.348
Everybody reads Bible, everybody reads Koran,

00:12:48.548 --> 00:12:51.880
but nothing goes inside just reading, reading, reading.

00:12:52.081 --> 00:12:54.450
So their idea is that if they read and analyze,

00:12:54.650 --> 00:12:57.049
I mean you have to have big universities for that,

00:12:57.249 --> 00:13:01.721
it could be taught to people and, still then not necessary,

00:13:01.921 --> 00:13:06.261
that they would imbibe.

00:13:06.912 --> 00:13:11.298
I know of Mahatma Gandhi, you  see, he was a realized soul himself

00:13:11.498 --> 00:13:16.935
and he was, of course, over-disciplined according to Me.

00:13:17.136 --> 00:13:23.692
And he put these ideas on to his followers.
As long as he lived, they were all right.

00:13:23.893 --> 00:13:27.573
As soon as he died, they came out in their true colors.

00:13:27.774 --> 00:13:31.921
Everything dropped off like some sort of a mud on their body,

00:13:32.121 --> 00:13:35.161
and they became horrible people in India.

00:13:35.362 --> 00:13:42.066
So the thing missing is this, that they are not realized souls.

00:13:42.267 --> 00:13:46.530
Because they are not Realized, all these things they cannot bear.

00:13:46.731 --> 00:13:49.432
They cannot bear money, they cannot bear power.

00:13:49.632 --> 00:13:54.273
Now I think, they cannot bear the religion.

00:13:54.474 --> 00:13:58.326
So you have to have your Realization.

00:13:58.527 --> 00:14:03.476
Unless and until you have your Realization, you cannot bear anything.

00:14:03.677 --> 00:14:09.482
Moreover in Sahaja Yoga I mean there are no
compulsions, no disciplines as such, I mean,

00:14:09.683 --> 00:14:14.929
compared to what we see in all these religions.

00:14:15.130 --> 00:14:18.417
Suddenly I find people coming up

00:14:18.617 --> 00:14:27.380
to the expectations of righteousness, goodness, and they are also very compassionate.

00:14:29.309 --> 00:14:33.444
So the change has come from inside, that means

00:14:33.645 --> 00:14:38.323
it’s the innate change. The innate religion has been awakened.

00:14:38.524 --> 00:14:42.880
It’s not just forced on you, that you should be Vishwa Nirmala Dharmis,

00:14:43.080 --> 00:14:46.221
but you become, you just become that.

00:14:46.422 --> 00:14:49.278
This is the point you will see, these Prophets did not know,

00:14:49.478 --> 00:14:52.853
I think Christ did not know that these people will never change

00:14:53.053 --> 00:14:57.555
unless and until they get their Realization.

00:14:57.756 --> 00:15:01.373
I think He knew also because He always said that you have to be born again.

00:15:01.574 --> 00:15:06.157
So when He said: ‘You are to be born again,’ they have a brand,

00:15:06.357 --> 00:15:10.071
you see again, one are Christian, he is a Born Again,

00:15:10.271 --> 00:15:12.732
another are Seventh Day, another, something.

00:15:12.933 --> 00:15:16.843
All just the same stupid people.

00:15:17.044 --> 00:15:23.962
But Sahaja Yoga is the only way, where what you say that’s what you follow.

00:15:24.163 --> 00:15:27.550
Practice and precepts are just the same for Sahaja Yogis.

00:15:27.751 --> 00:15:30.732
They just can’t do it something else.

00:15:30.933 --> 00:15:34.108
They are dreaming also that the occident had a very bad influence

00:15:34.308 --> 00:15:38.154
on Islam and all that. I don’t think it’s that.

00:15:38.355 --> 00:15:41.520
You are coming from the occident, still you have jumped into

00:15:41.720 --> 00:15:45.776
the right culture of religion,

00:15:45.977 --> 00:15:50.994
when you understand what is righteousness what is good. You can bear it.

00:15:51.195 --> 00:15:54.179
You’re not to be told do this, do that,

00:15:54.379 --> 00:15:57.769
but in the light of your Spirit, you do it.

00:15:57.971 --> 00:16:01.452
And you achieve it.

00:16:01.653 --> 00:16:06.514
It’s a very interesting thing to note

00:16:06.714 --> 00:16:09.694
that a little thing was missing in all of them,

00:16:09.894 --> 00:16:15.631
and they just went away as if they never knew where to land.

00:16:15.832 --> 00:16:20.190
All these religions, one better than the other.

00:16:20.391 --> 00:16:23.867
Hindus, same thing. Hindus had of course one advantage,

00:16:24.067 --> 00:16:26.812
they were never organized, thank God, because if you are organized

00:16:27.012 --> 00:16:31.217
and misled, then the whole party goes astray.

00:16:31.418 --> 00:16:35.280
But Hindus, Hindu scriptures were never organized

00:16:35.480 --> 00:16:40.445
into a religion like that. But still, so many points they have missed.

00:16:40.646 --> 00:16:45.427
Like it is said that: "In everyone there resides the Spirit".

00:16:45.628 --> 00:16:50.889
Then how can you have caste system? You cannot.

00:16:51.526 --> 00:16:54.217
But they have caste system.

00:16:54.417 --> 00:17:00.013
So, also so many other rituals and things nonsense is there,

00:17:00.213 --> 00:17:02.213
absolutely nonsense.

00:17:02.414 --> 00:17:12.714
And Hindu religion became a kind of a ritualistic religion,

00:17:12.914 --> 00:17:19.622
where the priests, uneducated useless priests became in charge.

00:17:19.823 --> 00:17:23.592
And they’re so stupid, worse than pope sometimes,

00:17:23.792 --> 00:17:26.392
that they say that if you want to have…

00:17:26.597 --> 00:17:29.147
Whose child is this one? Hello.

00:17:29.347 --> 00:17:31.561
You asked for to go back.

00:17:31.761 --> 00:17:34.904
You shoudn't talk, you should keep quiet

00:17:35.105 --> 00:17:39.510
Will you pleas go back?

00:17:39.950 --> 00:17:43.711
Only childrem who can sit quiet should come forward.

00:17:43.911 --> 00:17:47.903
Alright? Sit down.

00:17:55.151 --> 00:17:59.254
I’ve also found out a solution for children, our western children,

00:17:59.455 --> 00:18:03.667
what is the problem.

00:18:03.875 --> 00:18:08.760
I went to Japan and what I found there

00:18:08.960 --> 00:18:13.522
that till the age of twelve years, they don’t allow children to have

00:18:13.723 --> 00:18:19.259
much sports, to go out much, and mostly they are in the house

00:18:19.460 --> 00:18:24.894
or in the school, learning to do things with their hands.

00:18:25.095 --> 00:18:29.054
And medically I know that, till the age of twelve years,

00:18:29.254 --> 00:18:34.267
there is myelin sheath that grows on your nerves.

00:18:34.468 --> 00:18:38.528
And this myelin sheath gives you the deftness.

00:18:38.729 --> 00:18:41.840
Like if you go to the villages like Saranti or all these,

00:18:42.040 --> 00:18:47.301
where they are producing artistic things, what happens

00:18:47.501 --> 00:18:50.010
that the children also start doing the same.

00:18:50.211 --> 00:18:52.502
It’s so easy for them when they grow up.

00:18:52.702 --> 00:18:56.492
So that is the time when they have to develop that deftness.

00:18:56.693 --> 00:19:01.723
That deftness is, also makes them more concentrated,

00:19:01.923 --> 00:19:09.608
they get involved into it and also that you can never acquire later.

00:19:09.809 --> 00:19:12.705
So that is just a precious time of twelve years

00:19:12.905 --> 00:19:17.874
that that is the time children should be made to do some drawings,

00:19:18.075 --> 00:19:23.060
not at random, but properly, to do some carvings,

00:19:23.260 --> 00:19:26.246
to do some other clay work.

00:19:26.447 --> 00:19:28.849
You’ll be surprised by the age of twelve years,

00:19:29.049 --> 00:19:32.586
the boys in Japan could repair a watch,

00:19:32.787 --> 00:19:37.525
could repair televisions, and one boy produced, produced.

00:19:37.726 --> 00:19:40.961
At that time when I had gone, there were not many televisions also.

00:19:41.162 --> 00:19:45.743
I was surprised that the boy produced a television,

00:19:45.943 --> 00:19:49.281
at the age of twelve years. And also they are given violins

00:19:49.482 --> 00:19:53.636
in their hands when they’re about five years. They start playing.

00:19:53.837 --> 00:19:58.548
So the music, art and all this side is developed till the age of twelve years.

00:19:58.749 --> 00:20:01.374
And then the children are made to go out and play

00:20:01.574 --> 00:20:06.769
and do all kinds of exercises and also sports.

00:20:06.970 --> 00:20:12.644
But they are not let loose at a young age.

00:20:12.845 --> 00:20:15.036
Now here I think about twenty years back

00:20:15.236 --> 00:20:21.003
or may be twenty-five years back, a new theme started with children

00:20:21.203 --> 00:20:23.680
that, you should allow the children to do what they like,

00:20:23.880 --> 00:20:29.334
let them express themselves, let them be free, this that.

00:20:29.535 --> 00:20:32.736
I think it’s not proper. Otherwise they would be hanging

00:20:32.936 --> 00:20:35.691
from some trees trying to do without parents you see.

00:20:35.892 --> 00:20:40.371
After all this is the way the parents escape their duty, I think.

00:20:40.572 --> 00:20:44.139
You have to tell children what they have to do.

00:20:44.340 --> 00:20:49.458
You have to, talk to them, you must have a rapport with them.

00:20:49.659 --> 00:20:55.206
You must talk to them and you must also try to guide them,

00:20:55.407 --> 00:20:59.214
with your experience, tell them what is good what is bad.

00:20:59.415 --> 00:21:03.168
But this kind of a thing that the child should be allowed to do

00:21:03.368 --> 00:21:08.060
what they like, express themselves the way they like.

00:21:08.261 --> 00:21:11.300
I’ve seen the western children always will ask parents: ‘Why,

00:21:11.501 --> 00:21:15.933
why?’ They are not to know, they have limitations.

00:21:16.134 --> 00:21:19.191
They can’t know every ‘why’. How can they understand?

00:21:19.392 --> 00:21:23.500
They are limited and so, first of all, they are to build up.

00:21:23.701 --> 00:21:26.613
You can you see this aeroplane now. Supposing it is not built up

00:21:26.814 --> 00:21:33.296
and allowed to go because: "It’s all right. Let it go in the sky".

00:21:33.497 --> 00:21:35.975
What will happen?

00:21:36.176 --> 00:21:39.822
In the same way we have to put the nuts and bolts properly

00:21:40.022 --> 00:21:46.225
into them and see that they develop a personality.

00:21:46.426 --> 00:21:49.425
That doesn’t mean that you should be in any way cruel to them.

00:21:49.626 --> 00:21:54.636
Not necessary. There’s no need to beat them or do anything of the kind.

00:21:54.837 --> 00:21:59.783
But only thing is, with love, you should be able to explain to them.

00:21:59.992 --> 00:22:03.142
And also dignity, sense of dignity should be there.

00:22:03.343 --> 00:22:07.054
Because if you develop their sense of dignity, they will not misbehave.

00:22:07.255 --> 00:22:10.632
That’s very important from childhood to give them a sense of dignity,

00:22:10.833 --> 00:22:14.780
that they are Sahaja Yogis and they have to behave.

00:22:14.981 --> 00:22:19.373
Because when we started this school one year, first year,

00:22:19.573 --> 00:22:24.442
one month, it was such a problem, I mean, impossible situation.

00:22:24.642 --> 00:22:27.972
The teachers gave up and they wrote to Me:

00:22:28.172 --> 00:22:32.311
"Better send typhoon take children." It’s terrible. but they used to beat them

00:22:32.512 --> 00:22:36.279
Not only that, they trouble them, but they used to beat them

00:22:36.480 --> 00:22:41.799
and bite them and do all kinds of
thing and make fun of them. So wild.

00:22:42.000 --> 00:22:45.166
And that place is full of cliffs and full of

00:22:45.366 --> 00:22:49.788
all kinds of dangerous heights and they would just run out.

00:22:49.989 --> 00:22:53.121
Just like dogs. Dogs are better I would say.

00:22:53.322 --> 00:22:56.896
They had no caution about themselves and for one month,

00:22:57.096 --> 00:23:00.152
they all gave up. And the principal has now run away, he said: "I can’t manage

00:23:00.353 --> 00:23:04.201
these children, they don’t want to study.
They have come here to trouble us, that’s all.

00:23:04.402 --> 00:23:07.759
They don’t want to study." And first thing when I met them,

00:23:07.960 --> 00:23:13.714
they came and told Me: "Mother, we don’t want to study."

00:23:14.652 --> 00:23:18.706
Now we have put a one masseur on them,

00:23:18.907 --> 00:23:21.602
who massages their body. He was telling Me:

00:23:21.803 --> 00:23:24.549
"They are really funny children, they don’t want to brush their teeth.

00:23:24.750 --> 00:23:26.791
If you ask them to brush their teeth they start crying.

00:23:26.992 --> 00:23:29.851
They don’t want to have a bath. Tell them 'you have to have your bath',

00:23:30.052 --> 00:23:34.842
they start crying. Anything you tell them they start doing like that."

00:23:35.042 --> 00:23:39.840
So we can say one thing, that disciplining children in a indirect way

00:23:40.040 --> 00:23:43.127
is very important like that, you see.

00:23:43.328 --> 00:23:46.215
Because this idea, that you should leave the children as they are,

00:23:46.415 --> 00:23:51.878
is very wrong. You have to guide them and tell them how to behave.

00:23:52.079 --> 00:23:55.761
Now see, you must have seen Indian children how quiet they are.

00:23:55.961 --> 00:23:58.923
But I think the attention of children is quite a lot.

00:23:59.124 --> 00:24:04.352
And the mothers are not working also, so they look after the children.

00:24:04.552 --> 00:24:09.338
Now in our schools that we have here, you should train them up that way.

00:24:09.539 --> 00:24:14.423
You can talk to them that: "You are Sahaja Yogis, you see, you are special people."

00:24:14.624 --> 00:24:18.320
The other day there was one Indian child, he’s living in Singapore,

00:24:18.530 --> 00:24:21.352
where he has picked up all these bad habits.

00:24:21.553 --> 00:24:26.348
He came and he was talking to Me: ‘Grandma, Grandma.’

00:24:26.549 --> 00:24:30.672
And he said: "I will tell you in Your ear something".

00:24:30.873 --> 00:24:34.252
And he said something funny. I said: "Are you a servant?"

00:24:34.453 --> 00:24:36.922
He said: "No." "Then only servants talk like this.

00:24:37.122 --> 00:24:40.432
How are you talking like this?" "Is it?" I said: "Yes.

00:24:40.633 --> 00:24:43.755
This is how the servants talk." He got such a fright.

00:24:43.956 --> 00:24:46.721
He said: "All right, I will never talk like that. It’s dirty.

00:24:46.922 --> 00:24:50.651
I’ll not talk like that." You see, suddenly he changed.

00:24:50.851 --> 00:24:54.012
So we have to talk to them, we have to have rapport with them.

00:24:54.213 --> 00:24:59.869
After all they are born realized so they have special powers and they are special children.

00:25:00.070 --> 00:25:04.808
But ne thing is definite, that children cannot be avoided,

00:25:05.008 --> 00:25:10.032
and you cannot avoid your duty towards
your children. You have to look after them,

00:25:10.232 --> 00:25:14.320
because they are in your trust as it is. They are after all born

00:25:14.520 --> 00:25:17.336
Realized children. They are special children with tremendous brains.

00:25:17.536 --> 00:25:20.781
They are cleverer than you and they can outwit you,

00:25:20.981 --> 00:25:22.985
because they are so clever, so intelligent.

00:25:23.186 --> 00:25:26.520
But if they get spoiled at this age, then later on it will be very difficult

00:25:26.720 --> 00:25:30.450
to bring them. You were better, because you were not born

00:25:30.650 --> 00:25:34.040
with Realization. So you understood the value of Realization.

00:25:34.241 --> 00:25:36.260
But they don’t. So they are to be told that:

00:25:36.460 --> 00:25:40.172
"You are Realized children, God sent you here, you are special children,

00:25:40.373 --> 00:25:46.761
and what should happen." Gradually
they will pick up and understand.

00:25:46.961 --> 00:25:50.409
Of course I am happy that so many marriages are successful,

00:25:50.609 --> 00:25:53.314
and people are behaving all right. Of course there are

00:25:53.515 --> 00:25:56.946
some stray cases of fighting going on which I hear about.

00:25:57.147 --> 00:26:01.646
This is stupid of course again, that we should fight.

00:26:01.847 --> 00:26:03.982
When we are both Sahaja Yogis, what is there to fight?

00:26:04.183 --> 00:26:06.099
I mean, there’s no question.

00:26:06.300 --> 00:26:10.682
We believe in all the religions, so we can’t fight on religions.

00:26:10.882 --> 00:26:16.125
On what subject can we fight? I just don’t know.

00:26:21.474 --> 00:26:24.884
We know the ethics of Sahaja Yoga and we like it,

00:26:25.084 --> 00:26:27.648
so we cannot fight on ethics.

00:26:27.849 --> 00:26:31.582
Economics of Sahaja Yoga we understand, we cannot fight on that.

00:26:31.782 --> 00:26:35.252
I just don’t understand what is the difference,

00:26:35.452 --> 00:26:38.661
point of difference where they start fighting.

00:26:38.862 --> 00:26:43.578
On the contrary in Sahaja Yoga, you can really be

00:26:43.778 --> 00:26:47.523
enjoying your married life. Should be enjoying your married life

00:26:47.723 --> 00:26:54.457
and the children should see to it that "our
parents are so nicely, quietly settled down."

00:26:54.658 --> 00:26:59.680
But if they see you quarreling, next day they’ll be quarreling too.

00:26:59.881 --> 00:27:03.390
Then we have only monogamy. We don’t have three wives

00:27:03.591 --> 00:27:05.903
or four wives as the Muslims have.

00:27:06.104 --> 00:27:09.709
We don’t have four husbands or something like that.

00:27:09.910 --> 00:27:14.711
We have simple monogamy, a very peaceful life, very beautiful life,

00:27:14.911 --> 00:27:19.000
then why should there be problem between husband and wife?

00:27:19.201 --> 00:27:22.306
Culturally we are just the same, we believe in all the good cultures

00:27:22.506 --> 00:27:27.761
of all the world. There’s no problem.

00:27:31.269 --> 00:27:34.472
One gentleman told Me that: "My wife quarrels with Me on one point."

00:27:34.672 --> 00:27:39.471
I said: ‘Which?’ She said: "You do not meditate, you must meditate more."

00:27:39.672 --> 00:27:45.025
I said: ‘That’s a good point’. He thinks as well.

00:27:45.226 --> 00:27:48.534
But I told the wife that: "You need not tell him, he’ll do it on his own."

00:27:48.735 --> 00:27:53.002
Because you see cannot force things. This has to work out by themselves.

00:27:53.203 --> 00:27:56.486
You must accept them as they are. Gradually they’ll all improve

00:27:56.687 --> 00:28:01.266
and gradually they will get there.

00:28:01.880 --> 00:28:04.698
You cannot just force them.

00:28:04.899 --> 00:28:09.811
We cannot just tell each other, do this way or that way.

00:28:10.012 --> 00:28:16.420
Sahaja Yoga is a thing is to be imbibed. People don’t understand that.

00:28:16.621 --> 00:28:24.025
They think by forcing people, by jumping at them, that’s not the way.

00:28:24.226 --> 00:28:30.046
Of course if somebody is very difficult, then we have divorce in Sahaja Yoga.

00:28:30.247 --> 00:28:33.242
We have not banned divorce as in the Catholic religion or anything.

00:28:33.442 --> 00:28:37.143
There is divorce. But there should be something sensible about it.

00:28:37.344 --> 00:28:39.381
One has to work it out.

00:28:39.582 --> 00:28:43.688
Normally there should not be many cases of Sahaja Yoga, of divorce.

00:28:43.889 --> 00:28:46.877
But we have because of the background, certain types

00:28:47.077 --> 00:28:53.504
of funny relations they have had or I don’t know, what to say.

00:28:53.705 --> 00:29:01.357
On the whole, ninety percent or I should say
ninety-five percent marriages are quite successful,

00:29:01.557 --> 00:29:05.971
and will be more now the number will be much more, I’m sure.

00:29:06.172 --> 00:29:09.842
This time we had seventy-six marriages, so you can imagine.

00:29:10.042 --> 00:29:16.395
And in this one month, Yogi was after My life with his file there.

00:29:16.631 --> 00:29:23.705
So there also there’s some misunderstanding that Yogi decides, he does not, poor man.

00:29:23.906 --> 00:29:27.880
He cannot. But it happens sometimes, like at the last minute,

00:29:28.080 --> 00:29:32.754
they’ll bring somebody, now we cannot locate the name of that person,

00:29:32.955 --> 00:29:36.740
we just can’t find out if he’s there or not, or she’s there or not.

00:29:36.941 --> 00:29:41.369
Suddenly they bring somebody, and he may say or she may say

00:29:41.569 --> 00:29:45.172
that I am there on the form and all that. Then you have to accept it.

00:29:45.373 --> 00:29:47.766
If you accept such a thing then what happens

00:29:47.966 --> 00:29:50.883
that, you find that person is not a Sahaja Yogi

00:29:51.083 --> 00:29:55.049
or was not a Sahaja Yogi for such a long time. Something like that.

00:29:55.250 --> 00:29:59.766
So because of three hundred to four hundred requests, you see,

00:29:59.966 --> 00:30:06.341
what can we do. I mean after all, can’t know who is who.

00:30:06.542 --> 00:30:13.191
This is one thing that is very good.
At least we can control all that.

00:30:13.392 --> 00:30:17.890
If something is wrong, we can find out, we can work it out

00:30:18.090 --> 00:30:22.532
and we can manage things. It’s not so difficult.

00:30:22.733 --> 00:30:25.919
But the leaders must be careful because the leaders who recommend

00:30:26.119 --> 00:30:31.589
should not do something out of just some sort of a pity,

00:30:31.789 --> 00:30:36.268
or some sort of a consideration. The main consideration should be,

00:30:36.469 --> 00:30:40.170
how are the vibrations and what is the commitment in Sahaja Yoga.

00:30:40.371 --> 00:30:43.961
If they are committed to Sahaja Yoga and if their vibrations are all right,

00:30:44.161 --> 00:30:48.246
then it’s all right, it’s perfect. But sometimes, you know,

00:30:48.447 --> 00:30:55.806
some people do have problems which do not come up and later on it is discovered.

00:30:56.007 --> 00:31:00.132
Still, I am so happy our society is so great.

00:31:00.332 --> 00:31:03.264
There’s no such society existing in the whole world.

00:31:03.465 --> 00:31:07.771
And this is the society I think all these Prophets and everybody dreamt of,

00:31:07.972 --> 00:31:13.473
of such love, understanding.

00:31:13.674 --> 00:31:19.744
Gradually I think we all will grow and grow and grow.

00:31:19.945 --> 00:31:24.214
The growth is going on, but the atmosphere I must say is very nice,

00:31:24.414 --> 00:31:28.539
and it helps each other.

00:31:31.545 --> 00:31:35.880
In Australia we had more problems in Melbourne, not in Sydney,

00:31:36.080 --> 00:31:43.899
I must give credit to your leader here, he has managed the things well.

00:31:51.999 --> 00:31:55.571
There are many after him also it’s rather funny but I just don’t know,

00:31:55.771 --> 00:31:59.743
because Australia always had a problem, this kind

00:31:59.943 --> 00:32:04.219
and gradually we have sorted it out.

00:32:04.420 --> 00:32:07.881
It’s a, leadership means nothing but I call it hocus-pocus.

00:32:08.082 --> 00:32:13.502
It has no meaning at all. But then somebody
has to be there to contact and all that.

00:32:13.702 --> 00:32:17.866
It’s something so limited.

00:32:18.067 --> 00:32:22.962
But there is jealousy, there is all these things stil lingering behind

00:32:23.212 --> 00:32:27.812
and then the problems come in.

00:32:28.040 --> 00:32:32.323
Gradually I am sure all of us will grow well and everything will work out

00:32:32.523 --> 00:32:36.393
in a proper way. Should work out in a proper way.

00:32:36.594 --> 00:32:44.158
Our society has to show to the world that there can be a society like this.

00:32:44.359 --> 00:32:49.532
Now there’s a good news which is very good, I think,

00:32:49.732 --> 00:32:52.110
we can start the calendar from that date perhaps

00:32:52.310 --> 00:32:55.080
because such a transformation is coming,

00:32:55.280 --> 00:32:59.279
that the Russian Embassy has invited Me to honor Me

00:32:59.487 --> 00:33:03.659
for the work I have done in Russia.

00:33:18.032 --> 00:33:22.694
And the another good news is that Gorbachov wants to meet Me.

00:33:37.138 --> 00:33:40.414
And you must be aware that in Tagliatti, is one place,

00:33:40.614 --> 00:33:44.764
Tagliatti which is an industrial town where a gentleman called Pagliati

00:33:44.964 --> 00:33:49.018
from Italy went down, he was a revolutionary.

00:33:49.219 --> 00:33:56.659
And he started this place called as Togliati and the best motorcar

00:33:56.859 --> 00:33:59.774
that they make is made in this place Tagliatti, beautiful one.

00:33:59.975 --> 00:34:03.983
They gave Me a model here, very beautiful, quite big. Is like a limousine.

00:34:04.184 --> 00:34:10.828
Quite big. And in that one city,

00:34:11.028 --> 00:34:17.603
we have twenty-two thousand Sahaja Yogis practising, twenty-two thousand.

00:34:17.804 --> 00:34:22.478
And you’ll be amazed that in Russia nowhere is less than

00:34:22.678 --> 00:34:26.531
sixteen thousand people, nowhere. Any time you go there,

00:34:26.732 --> 00:34:31.108
at least sixteen thousand people practising Sahaja Yoga, very seriously.

00:34:31.309 --> 00:34:33.352
So can imagine in that country what is going to happen,

00:34:33.552 --> 00:34:37.539
though it hasn’t got food as you have here, too much to eat,

00:34:37.739 --> 00:34:45.198
but still look at the way, look at the way it has worked out.

00:34:45.399 --> 00:34:47.457
How deeply they have gone into it.

00:34:47.658 --> 00:34:51.074
They had never heard a word about Ganesha.

00:34:51.275 --> 00:34:54.951
They never believed in God. They were in a way atheist.

00:34:55.151 --> 00:34:58.041
And how much they have achieved in just…look at that.

00:34:58.242 --> 00:35:02.954
How did they achieve that? The depth that they have,

00:35:03.154 --> 00:35:07.517
they just touched it. And also they invited some scientist,

00:35:07.717 --> 00:35:11.200
or two hundred scientists were there. And when I started telling about science,

00:35:11.401 --> 00:35:14.176
said: "Mother, don’t tell us about science, had enough of it.

00:35:14.377 --> 00:35:17.972
Now please tell us about Spiritual science, spirituality. That’s all."

00:35:18.173 --> 00:35:20.891
Wonderful I tell you, such experiences.

00:35:21.092 --> 00:35:24.378
And in My lecture only, just giving a lecture at the time

00:35:24.578 --> 00:35:28.222
when there were about sixteen thousand to eighteen thousand people,

00:35:28.422 --> 00:35:31.627
people got cured, just got cured.

00:35:31.828 --> 00:35:35.199
Such wonders. There was one lady who came to see Me

00:35:35.399 --> 00:35:40.041
after the lecture and she was just sitting in front of Me.

00:35:40.242 --> 00:35:43.530
They brought her on a wheelchair. She said: "I couldn’t even sit."

00:35:43.731 --> 00:35:47.280
All right. And then I said: "You are all right". She said: "Really?"

00:35:47.481 --> 00:35:51.164
I said: "Yes. You get up." Got up. She started walking

00:35:51.365 --> 00:35:55.511
and then she started running and everybody started…

00:35:55.712 --> 00:36:00.821
Such faith, such faith. And in
Czechoslovakia, there was one old lady.

00:36:01.022 --> 00:36:05.103
They brought her with great difficulty just, held her out

00:36:05.303 --> 00:36:10.295
and brought her on the stage and she was trying to sit down.

00:36:10.496 --> 00:36:13.785
Then she said: "Mother I have complete faith in You.

00:36:13.986 --> 00:36:16.783
I know You can cure Me." I said "Really?"

00:36:16.984 --> 00:36:19.174
"Yes. I am sure You can."

00:36:19.375 --> 00:36:24.625
I said:"You are cured." She got up. Everybody was surprised.

00:36:24.852 --> 00:36:26.852
I said: "Now walk. Walk now."

00:36:27.053 --> 00:36:32.101
And then she started walking fast, and everybody started laughing.

00:36:32.302 --> 00:36:36.689
But that faith, you see, is something so special.

00:36:36.890 --> 00:36:42.439
I mean I have seen so many miracles happening with this faith that…

00:36:42.640 --> 00:36:45.682
There was one fellow called Mr Shukla,

00:36:45.882 --> 00:36:52.698
who is a big boss in this hotel management of Taj Mahal.

00:36:52.899 --> 00:36:57.590
And this Mr Shukla heard that his mother was very sick,

00:36:57.790 --> 00:37:00.711
she was going to die. Very serious.

00:37:00.912 --> 00:37:05.798
So he went to Rotak which is very far away, beyond Delhi from Mumbai,

00:37:05.998 --> 00:37:10.089
and he saw his mother in a very bad condition, very painful.

00:37:10.290 --> 00:37:14.973
The doctor said she has a galloping cancer and at the most,

00:37:15.173 --> 00:37:19.290
she can live for three days. He got very much worried.

00:37:19.491 --> 00:37:22.000
He came back home. He thought that:

00:37:22.200 --> 00:37:24.766
"I couldn’t even talk to my mother, she’s in a coma,

00:37:24.966 --> 00:37:29.991
what will happen to her?" He just sat before My photograph

00:37:30.192 --> 00:37:33.225
and prayed: "Mother, please cure my mother.

00:37:33.426 --> 00:37:37.936
I don’t want anything just now, You just cure my mother, I know You can cure her."

00:37:38.137 --> 00:37:40.781
And within three days before, instead of dying,

00:37:40.981 --> 00:37:45.155
she was out of the hospital. He brought her to Mumbai.

00:37:45.356 --> 00:37:48.539
They took her to the hospital of Thata, Thata Memorial Hospital

00:37:48.739 --> 00:37:54.342
we have, and when they examined her they said, she has no cancer.

00:37:54.542 --> 00:38:00.661
He has papers. He has papers from the first hospital and from this one.

00:38:00.862 --> 00:38:03.279
Recently, Rajesh told Me a story about himself.

00:38:03.480 --> 00:38:06.255
He said: ‘Mother, You don’t know how many powers You have given me.’

00:38:06.456 --> 00:38:10.216
I said: "No it’s your faith." His uncle was just dying.

00:38:10.417 --> 00:38:12.693
They had removed his oxygen and everything.

00:38:12.895 --> 00:38:16.411
His aunt sent for him and she said: "Now he’s about to die.

00:38:16.612 --> 00:38:20.373
You pray for his salvation, at least to Mother.

00:38:20.574 --> 00:38:26.988
Just somehow or other try to see that he’s also gets his salvation".

00:38:27.189 --> 00:38:30.200
He’s not a Sahaja Yogi uncle nothing of the kind.

00:38:30.401 --> 00:38:36.506
So Rajesh just had his pendant, just twisted it,

00:38:36.706 --> 00:38:42.440
and then closed his eyes and prayed: "Mother, please cure my uncle."

00:38:42.641 --> 00:38:47.493
That’s all. He said "it was too much of a venture to say but I did say".

00:38:47.694 --> 00:38:52.010
And the uncle who was dying got all right, went to America

00:38:52.210 --> 00:38:55.763
and he’s back and still kicking.

00:38:55.964 --> 00:39:02.661
So this is something you see we
have to go deep down into ourselves.

00:39:02.862 --> 00:39:05.605
Superficiality is not going to help us.

00:39:05.806 --> 00:39:09.538
If we are superficial by nature, it will not help us.

00:39:09.739 --> 00:39:13.491
We have to understand ourselves. The whole mechanism is within us

00:39:13.692 --> 00:39:16.918
to attract the attention of this All-Pervading Power,

00:39:17.119 --> 00:39:21.012
to use it, to work it out. We can do marvels.

00:39:21.213 --> 00:39:27.083
If we really go deep down, and become good vehicles of that All-Pervading Power.

00:39:27.284 --> 00:39:32.674
That’s what we have to do. Everything can
work out. There are so many examples of this,

00:39:32.875 --> 00:39:38.671
but specially these two recently I heard about and I was amazed.

00:39:38.872 --> 00:39:42.281
We have to have that depth within us to understand:

00:39:42.482 --> 00:39:46.482
"What are we doing?" "Where are we?"

00:39:46.682 --> 00:39:51.074
"We are born at this time, such an important time."

00:39:51.275 --> 00:39:55.561
"And that at this time, we have got Self-realization."

00:39:55.761 --> 00:39:59.993
Very few people got it. Not only that,

00:40:00.193 --> 00:40:04.532
we have been blessed with so many things.

00:40:04.733 --> 00:40:07.480
But above all we are so powerful.

00:40:07.681 --> 00:40:12.260
And all these powers must be manifested, must be used,

00:40:12.461 --> 00:40:15.550
must be worked out.

00:40:15.751 --> 00:40:20.729
And this superficiality of living on a very mundane style

00:40:20.929 --> 00:40:24.073
is not going to help us.

00:40:24.274 --> 00:40:27.638
We have to really go deep down into ourselves.

00:40:27.839 --> 00:40:30.747
I mean you are seekers, no doubt, you are seekers of truth.

00:40:30.948 --> 00:40:33.990
And you have found it also. How many have found it?

00:40:34.191 --> 00:40:37.918
So many are already lost if you see as hippies, as this, as that,

00:40:38.119 --> 00:40:40.624
as TM, as another this Rajneesh.

00:40:40.824 --> 00:40:43.880
I’ve seen some other lady here, two months she came.

00:40:44.080 --> 00:40:47.406
How much she was caught up. She was just worried.

00:40:47.607 --> 00:40:51.156
So many are lost like that. But you are the people who have got

00:40:51.357 --> 00:40:54.976
the knowledge, you are God’s people, you have got the truth with you,

00:40:55.177 --> 00:40:58.537
and all these powers are within you, but you must use them.

00:40:58.738 --> 00:41:02.108
But I’ve seen even after coming to Sahaja Yoga some people get lost

00:41:02.308 --> 00:41:04.316
in the temptation because they get money.

00:41:04.517 --> 00:41:07.300
Some people get some talents, they get lost in the talents.

00:41:07.501 --> 00:41:10.268
Some people get some powers, they’ll get lost with them.

00:41:10.469 --> 00:41:13.545
That’s not the way.

00:41:13.747 --> 00:41:18.533
You see if God has given you this Realization, He expects you

00:41:18.733 --> 00:41:22.834
to give Realizations to others, to go deep down into your Self.

00:41:23.035 --> 00:41:28.660
This is what we have to do is to really work out, our depth.

00:41:28.861 --> 00:41:32.920
And it all exists within us. You never knew there is Spirit within us.

00:41:33.120 --> 00:41:36.963
Is there. You never knew there is Ganesha within us. Is there.

00:41:37.261 --> 00:41:43.561
And when you started awakening them, you found it works, it works.

00:41:43.761 --> 00:41:49.321
It has worked such wonders, health wise, wealth wise, in every way.

00:41:49.521 --> 00:41:52.511
But spiritually, how far we are?

00:41:52.712 --> 00:41:55.985
How do you judge a person who is spiritually evolved?

00:41:56.185 --> 00:42:01.745
Is that, even a desire works out.

00:42:02.386 --> 00:42:05.654
Any, desire works out.

00:42:05.855 --> 00:42:09.573
And such a person doesn’t have any funny desires.

00:42:09.774 --> 00:42:12.729
Absolutely it works out.

00:42:12.930 --> 00:42:15.880
And that’s what I want Australians to do because

00:42:16.080 --> 00:42:20.124
you are special people born in this country of Ganesha.

00:42:20.325 --> 00:42:24.602
Perhaps we forget sometimes that you are born

00:42:24.802 --> 00:42:30.340
in the land of Shri Ganesha. Very special people.

00:42:30.541 --> 00:42:33.493
Very special. So have respect for yourself.

00:42:33.694 --> 00:42:38.736
And also must manifest your glory.

00:42:38.937 --> 00:42:42.153
That otherwise, of all the places from Russia,

00:42:42.353 --> 00:42:45.826
Sahaja Yoga will spread, it’s not, I mean, never expected that.

00:42:46.027 --> 00:42:49.120
But it may, it may, I tell you they are so deep,

00:42:49.321 --> 00:42:53.808
so very deep people, extremely deep.

00:42:54.009 --> 00:42:56.065
I don’t know what has given this.

00:42:56.266 --> 00:42:59.836
Materialism I think is responsible for our superficiality.

00:43:00.037 --> 00:43:02.437
They are not materialistic.

00:43:02.638 --> 00:43:06.492
About thirty percent people are materialistic, the rest are not.

00:43:06.693 --> 00:43:10.137
They are all seeking the spirit in the real sense of the word.

00:43:10.338 --> 00:43:13.811
Not just for fashion.

00:43:14.012 --> 00:43:16.754
Very remarkable.

00:43:16.955 --> 00:43:24.789
Very loving. Very beautiful. I was there, they came.

00:43:24.990 --> 00:43:29.851
They arranged that, from one place,

00:43:30.052 --> 00:43:33.675
some people will come only for two days then two days.

00:43:33.876 --> 00:43:38.257
And where I had purchased a little cottage, they,

00:43:38.457 --> 00:43:42.771
there are some places where they can live in a small little huts like that.

00:43:42.972 --> 00:43:45.906
They all came and stayed there. I didn’t know where they were living

00:43:46.107 --> 00:43:49.024
or anything. Early in the morning they would come,

00:43:49.224 --> 00:43:54.685
bring some flowers, and plant the flowers in the garden, flowers, itself.

00:43:54.886 --> 00:43:59.254
And would not say anything and go away. Sit down for meditation.

00:43:59.455 --> 00:44:02.527
One day suddenly I discovered all of them sitting there meditating.

00:44:02.728 --> 00:44:08.699
So surprised. And then it was this Gorbachov problems came up.

00:44:08.900 --> 00:44:11.259
So I said: "Now what are you going to do?" "What are we doing?

00:44:11.460 --> 00:44:14.092
We are in the kingdom of God. Why should we worry about Gorbachov

00:44:14.293 --> 00:44:19.231
or anyone, why should we? We are not worried."

00:44:19.431 --> 00:44:24.700
Beautiful people. Beautiful.

00:44:24.900 --> 00:44:30.226
Very collective. Also this is the blessing of communism, they are very collective.

00:44:30.427 --> 00:44:34.339
I have seen that also in Calcutta.
People are extremely collective.

00:44:34.539 --> 00:44:40.067
They don’t talk ill of others. Very collective people.

00:44:41.372 --> 00:44:45.467
It’s not like: "Come to my house. Oh You must visit. This thing,

00:44:45.668 --> 00:44:49.590
this is my daughter." That ‘my-ness’
I didn’t see, in Russia and in Calcutta.

00:44:49.791 --> 00:44:55.904
I was surprised. Calcutta also has communistic, communist government.

00:44:56.105 --> 00:45:00.506
How it has worked out, I can’t say.

00:45:03.942 --> 00:45:08.771
So are you spreading Sahaja Yoga?

00:45:08.972 --> 00:45:13.401
How many people give Realization?

00:45:22.589 --> 00:45:25.385
Now you are doing.

00:45:25.586 --> 00:45:29.706
You all have to do it. It’s very important.

00:45:34.251 --> 00:45:39.712
All of you should ask this question: "What have I done for God?"

00:45:44.541 --> 00:45:47.744
Look at these flowers that you brought.

00:45:47.945 --> 00:45:50.891
They are so fragrant. They are so beautiful.

00:45:51.092 --> 00:45:56.015
They are going to live for a very short time. But what pleasure.

00:45:56.216 --> 00:46:02.097
What expression of your love they give. How beautiful they are.

00:46:07.171 --> 00:46:11.320
Australians have a very big role to play.

00:46:11.521 --> 00:46:17.195
As I expect from Ganesha, I expect from you also.

00:47:03.440 --> 00:47:07.911
Yogi: And they managed to get some editorial in the newspaper,

00:47:08.111 --> 00:47:11.638
for their programs as a run-up to Your visit.

00:47:11.838 --> 00:47:15.960
And in the first program they got sixty Chinese people,

00:47:16.160 --> 00:47:18.557
very good quality people.

00:47:18.766 --> 00:47:22.941
Shri Mataji: Oh Look at Alex.

00:47:23.141 --> 00:47:26.404
Alex is really special I must say.

00:47:26.605 --> 00:47:32.067
Such a beautiful boy. When his mother died,

00:47:32.268 --> 00:47:38.424
and he was staying with Me, so I said: "Alex won’t to go to your mother?"

00:47:38.625 --> 00:47:42.705
So he said: ‘Mother, there’s no seat available.

00:47:42.906 --> 00:47:45.312
Will take about four, five days to get a seat

00:47:45.513 --> 00:47:48.629
by the time will go home.

00:47:48.830 --> 00:47:53.822
So what is the need. I am with You.’

00:47:55.540 --> 00:47:59.768
I said: "You did try?" He said: "I did little bit, not much,

00:47:59.968 --> 00:48:03.861
because I saw You, and I knew that my mother will have Eternal life,

00:48:04.062 --> 00:48:06.937
so why should I worry?"

00:48:07.138 --> 00:48:13.388
Now he’s saying that Alex has got sixty Chinese people in Hong Kong.

00:48:13.589 --> 00:48:18.398
I couldn’t get even one.

00:48:27.881 --> 00:48:32.906
Chinese are another one. If Sahaja Yoga gets into their heads,

00:48:33.107 --> 00:48:42.001
they’re very traditional, very, very deep, very deep people, Chinese.

00:48:43.406 --> 00:48:47.628
The Prime Minister of China, I met him when I went there,

00:48:47.828 --> 00:48:52.240
in a photograph he’s just next to Me standing.

00:48:52.441 --> 00:48:57.809
After that he became Prime Minister, not that time. A very nice man.

00:48:58.010 --> 00:49:03.209
And he was asking Me about spiritual life, all the time.

00:49:03.410 --> 00:49:05.801
I showed complete ignorance, you see.

00:49:06.002 --> 00:49:09.172
I said 'these communists God knows what they are up to.

00:49:09.373 --> 00:49:13.971
I didn’t tell him. But I think we can approach him now.

00:49:14.172 --> 00:49:16.572
Somehow or another they got very fond of Me,

00:49:16.772 --> 00:49:20.342
all the Chinese government and all. Somehow.

00:49:20.543 --> 00:49:23.997
Some sort of an auspiciousness they felt about Me.

00:49:24.198 --> 00:49:31.936
I couldn’t understand them, what made them respect Me so much.

00:49:35.454 --> 00:49:41.293
They had one exhibition, one which they had invited Me and My husband,

00:49:41.494 --> 00:49:46.790
and I couldn’t go at this point. And the next day was closed

00:49:46.991 --> 00:49:51.108
that exhibition must be closed, but they kept it open for Me alone.

00:49:51.309 --> 00:49:54.900
And they said: "You must see the exhibition, it’s important."

00:49:55.101 --> 00:50:00.929
I don’t know, they have their own ways of understanding.

00:50:02.441 --> 00:50:08.227
We had Confucius there. They follow more Confucius now,

00:50:08.428 --> 00:50:16.144
our Confucius who has talked about general well-being and all that.

00:50:16.345 --> 00:50:22.790
But not so much about Tao, that they don’t talk.

00:50:28.204 --> 00:50:32.070
But they are extremely humble, Chinese. Very humble.

00:50:32.271 --> 00:50:35.380
You try to praise them and they say: ‘No, no.

00:50:35.581 --> 00:50:38.010
We have to do much better than this, nothing.’

00:50:38.211 --> 00:50:45.502
They can never get pampered, you see, you couldn’t praise them, never.

00:50:47.421 --> 00:50:52.788
They are very much like Russians in so many ways.

00:51:01.878 --> 00:51:05.840
I can see Sahaja Yogis here.

00:51:19.441 --> 00:51:26.752
So now, any questions?

00:51:32.740 --> 00:51:37.115
Tania is very happy with her husband. Very happy.

00:51:37.359 --> 00:51:40.632
She’s very happy.

00:51:40.906 --> 00:51:43.245
She has what?

00:51:43.445 --> 00:51:46.771
She too?

00:51:49.531 --> 00:51:57.457
I’ve told him what is the thing. Can you fax to Dr Spiro?

00:52:08.180 --> 00:52:12.539
She is on the liver

00:52:12.740 --> 00:52:16.677
or her husband was just like a child.

00:52:16.879 --> 00:52:22.019
But see him when he sings, absolutely.

00:52:22.220 --> 00:52:27.939
Remarkable. There’s that one with a super-intelligence I see.

00:52:29.491 --> 00:52:32.682
Wonderful.

00:52:34.411 --> 00:52:38.582
She’s happy because she can come to pujas, we are now there.

00:52:38.783 --> 00:52:42.413
She is very happy about that.

00:52:43.682 --> 00:52:45.908
She’s happy in Spain also.

00:52:46.109 --> 00:52:50.257
Italians are better but not Spanish people.

00:52:50.458 --> 00:52:53.805
Spanish are little bit - I think this American conquering

00:52:54.005 --> 00:52:58.938
has reflected in their character.

00:53:03.000 --> 00:53:07.840
There are also some misunderstanding of people think that

00:53:08.040 --> 00:53:12.191
I have said that the men should dominate women. Never.

00:53:12.392 --> 00:53:15.984
I am Myself a woman and then, if men start dominating Me,

00:53:16.184 --> 00:53:20.192
what will happen?

00:53:21.036 --> 00:53:25.530
But the man is the head of the family.

00:53:25.731 --> 00:53:29.773
So the woman should get her authority from him,

00:53:29.973 --> 00:53:33.125
but she has her own authority, as a mother,

00:53:33.326 --> 00:53:39.551
and the husband must respect her. Otherwise he’ll never be respected.

00:53:39.752 --> 00:53:43.411
So it’s kind of mutual understanding between the two, as I have said that

00:53:43.611 --> 00:53:47.971
they are the two wheels of a chariot, one on the left, one on the right.

00:53:48.171 --> 00:53:52.732
If you change the wheels, then what will happen?

00:53:52.933 --> 00:53:58.769
They are absolutely equal no doubt. Absolutely equal.

00:53:58.970 --> 00:54:03.282
Only they are not similar, which we must understand that we are not similar.

00:54:03.483 --> 00:54:07.659
Is nice to be a woman, I tell you, it’s much better.

00:54:07.860 --> 00:54:12.261
Because men have to face so many people, face so many bosses.

00:54:12.462 --> 00:54:18.893
You have only one "boss" and if you know how to manage him…

00:54:22.406 --> 00:54:26.835
But should be done sweetly, with understanding.

00:54:27.036 --> 00:54:32.404
It works out with your wisdom.

00:54:32.605 --> 00:54:35.016
Must have the wisdom, how to manage it.

00:54:35.218 --> 00:54:40.662
But that’s a part of the game and one has to play it well.

00:54:40.863 --> 00:54:44.318
Not to feel any way dominated by anything, but it’s a

00:54:44.518 --> 00:54:48.244
kind of a framework one has to work with.

00:54:48.445 --> 00:54:51.904
Now supposing this is on our head. This is not dominating us,

00:54:52.105 --> 00:54:54.574
but it has to be there.

00:54:54.775 --> 00:55:01.126
So a kind of a framework is there and that framework is to be accepted.

00:55:01.327 --> 00:55:04.245
Both of them should accept and the husband should never

00:55:04.445 --> 00:55:07.591
make her feel that he is dominating her.

00:55:07.792 --> 00:55:12.790
Actually, in India the custom is that husbands are also very clever,

00:55:12.990 --> 00:55:16.780
not only the women. So normally they’ll give all the money

00:55:16.981 --> 00:55:22.851
to the wife to be managed and later on take away all of that.

00:55:23.668 --> 00:55:27.889
And always they’ll say: "All right".

00:55:28.090 --> 00:55:31.308
They’ll say: "All right", the son to her like guru and all that.

00:55:31.509 --> 00:55:34.649
Means: "You are my lord and this and that and…"

00:55:34.850 --> 00:55:37.813
That’s how they keep it up.Because one thing they must understand

00:55:38.014 --> 00:55:41.529
is that if wife is all right, the family is all right.

00:55:41.730 --> 00:55:44.452
If wife is all right, your life is all right.

00:55:44.653 --> 00:55:48.309
So you must look after your wife, is very important.

00:55:48.510 --> 00:55:51.634
If you understand that point the men will never try to dominate.

00:55:51.835 --> 00:55:54.160
Is a wrong idea is, I don’t know from where it has trickled down

00:55:54.360 --> 00:55:58.001
that I have said, the man should dominate a woman.

00:55:58.202 --> 00:56:02.159
But false prestige should not be there.

00:56:02.360 --> 00:56:04.833
Like in America we went first.

00:56:05.034 --> 00:56:08.590
You know American women, how they are.

00:56:08.791 --> 00:56:13.044
They’ll divorce ten times and have all the money of the men.

00:56:13.245 --> 00:56:16.325
The men are just like beggars and they are so rich.

00:56:16.526 --> 00:56:22.127
It’s a profession with them. The women have this profession of divorcing men.

00:56:22.328 --> 00:56:25.211
So they had cooked and all that. So I said: "All right

00:56:25.411 --> 00:56:28.272
let the boys eat first and then you can eat later on."

00:56:28.472 --> 00:56:30.714
They said: "Mother this is domination." I said: "Why?

00:56:30.915 --> 00:56:33.516
Eating first is domination or later on domination."

00:56:33.717 --> 00:56:37.852
I think eating there later on is domination, because you are at peace, you see.

00:56:38.053 --> 00:56:42.040
Eat as much as you like.
But if somebody is eating first,

00:56:42.240 --> 00:56:46.501
then he’s in a hurry to finish for the next lot that has to come up.

00:56:46.702 --> 00:56:49.623
But if you are the second one, then you are relaxed,

00:56:49.823 --> 00:56:52.635
you are eating the way you like. There’s nothing to feed.

00:56:52.836 --> 00:56:56.217
And moreover, it’s an attitude I think

00:56:56.417 --> 00:57:00.922
that: "I love to cook, I love to serve, I enjoy it. I enjoy."

00:57:01.123 --> 00:57:06.907
It’s a, temperament of a woman. She
wants to feed people, she likes it.

00:57:07.108 --> 00:57:11.560
I tell you, My grandchildren, daughters, both of them,

00:57:11.760 --> 00:57:15.842
they were quite small, I asked them what do you want to be in life.

00:57:16.042 --> 00:57:20.194
So they said: "We want to be a nurse or an airhostess."

00:57:20.395 --> 00:57:22.411
So I said: "Why these two?"

00:57:22.612 --> 00:57:27.464
"In these only two professions, you can give food to people. That’s why."

00:57:27.665 --> 00:57:29.706
And they play, you know, they play like that.

00:57:29.907 --> 00:57:32.632
They’ll make a tray in that they will put this thing].

00:57:32.832 --> 00:57:35.781
So this is actually innate feeling of a child.

00:57:35.981 --> 00:57:40.011
Like once My daughter told that "if somebody comes from outside,

00:57:40.212 --> 00:57:42.425
you must make him sit on the sofa there.

00:57:42.626 --> 00:57:44.974
You must see that the fan is open.

00:57:45.175 --> 00:57:48.431
Give them something to eat, take out from the fridge" and all that.

00:57:48.632 --> 00:57:50.982
So one washerman, the dhobi came in.

00:57:51.183 --> 00:57:54.332
They called for [INAUDIBLE] to sit on the sofa. He said: "I can’t sit."

00:57:54.532 --> 00:57:57.508
"You have to sit." "I’m in a hurry." "Nothing you have to sit."

00:57:57.709 --> 00:58:01.160
They made him sit, opened the fan, got everything from the fridge,

00:58:01.360 --> 00:58:04.570
put it before him. "You have to eat, otherwise we’ll feed", you see.

00:58:04.771 --> 00:58:07.446
And when My daughter entered the house, she saw these girls

00:58:07.646 --> 00:58:11.909
feeding him with their own hands. Got such a fright.

00:58:12.110 --> 00:58:14.520
He said: "I’m sorry these girls, I don’t know what are they are."

00:58:14.721 --> 00:58:18.691
They said: "You told us and we’re very happy we are doing that."

00:58:18.892 --> 00:58:22.384
So innately children have this feeling in their hearts,

00:58:22.585 --> 00:58:27.920
as girls. And then when we
get a chance, we want to do it.

00:58:28.121 --> 00:58:32.936
I mean, it’s such a pleasure, to feed someone.

00:58:33.137 --> 00:58:35.343
You must have seen with Indian women, it’s very common,

00:58:35.543 --> 00:58:40.522
they love to feed others, they’re very happy.

00:58:44.041 --> 00:58:47.323
And, I mean there’s no domination I mean if you have to feed someone,

00:58:47.523 --> 00:58:49.894
that doesn’t mean that somebody’s dominating you,

00:58:50.094 --> 00:58:56.427
these are all nonsensical norms. On the contrary it’s a privilege.

00:58:56.628 --> 00:58:59.057
Otherwise after sometime, we’ll find

00:58:59.258 --> 00:59:02.999
that men will be sitting at home and the women will be going out.

00:59:03.199 --> 00:59:07.738
That will be, that’s already a situation, I mean.

00:59:16.989 --> 00:59:22.000
It’s hot for children I think, we are in a cabin.

00:59:22.200 --> 00:59:28.919
Like the ship, I think, without the sea.

00:59:38.883 --> 00:59:42.999
Entrepeneur.

00:59:46.638 --> 00:59:50.247
I see.

00:59:50.974 --> 00:59:54.982
It's quite a small book, I have to say.

01:00:04.056 --> 01:00:08.345
So what are they saying?

01:00:27.682 --> 01:00:30.966
It is a ???

01:00:31.182 --> 01:00:36.728
And then they say "You can do this, women can to this and..."

01:00:46.397 --> 01:00:50.795
It is very good.

01:00:56.293 --> 01:00:59.623
I know.

01:00:59.847 --> 01:01:03.562
You see in a - I can have the book?

01:01:03.762 --> 01:01:08.093
In Germany, when I went, there was a lady

01:01:08.293 --> 01:01:14.189
and she was telling Me that in Germany, if you get old,

01:01:14.389 --> 01:01:18.791
then the men go after younger girls and you are left alone.

01:01:18.991 --> 01:01:21.267
Then you have to marry some older man,

01:01:21.467 --> 01:01:24.797
who is left by his wife or something.

01:01:24.997 --> 01:01:27.941
It’s a big danger. I said: "Why don’t you produce children.

01:01:28.141 --> 01:01:30.976
I mean they get, if you have four children they get more money

01:01:31.177 --> 01:01:35.410
than the Prime Minister." They said: "But then you cannot have a husband."

01:01:35.611 --> 01:01:39.402
Either you have children or you have a husband. It’s like that.

01:01:39.602 --> 01:01:42.920
It is because, I tell you, it’s very superficial,

01:01:43.120 --> 01:01:49.192
very materialistic superficial ideas, about women also. They’re a commodity.

01:01:49.393 --> 01:01:56.023
In Sahaja Yoga woman, is a person as equal as a man, you see.

01:01:56.224 --> 01:01:58.109
It’s very different.

01:01:58.310 --> 01:02:04.716
They are just a commodity to be used, whenever they want to.

01:02:04.917 --> 01:02:08.533
And I must say also some women know the weaknesses of men

01:02:08.733 --> 01:02:12.607
and try to work it out in such a manner.

01:02:12.807 --> 01:02:17.161
Sometimes the women only trouble women, also.

01:02:17.362 --> 01:02:19.872
They don’t understand that "she’s a woman and I’m a woman,

01:02:20.072 --> 01:02:25.628
I should not try to trouble." But in sort of competitiveness,

01:02:25.829 --> 01:02:31.012
they do wrong things and try to destroy another’s life.

01:02:31.213 --> 01:02:34.276
But men will have to change now, it’s coming to that.

01:02:34.476 --> 01:02:39.867
All these tricks they have tried and they are now having lot of problem.

01:02:40.067 --> 01:02:45.142
There are diseases that are coming up. Already
there’s lots of already these secret diseases there.

01:02:45.351 --> 01:02:48.094
Apart from these secret diseases, there are diseases

01:02:48.294 --> 01:02:51.501
which are coping them, new diseases.

01:02:51.702 --> 01:02:54.320
So now they’ll have to come to monogamy.

01:02:54.521 --> 01:02:56.807
Once they come to monogamy, then they’ll have to realize

01:02:57.007 --> 01:03:00.215
the value of women, what they are.

01:03:00.416 --> 01:03:08.084
And in this all quarrel about ordination.

01:03:08.284 --> 01:03:11.060
Imagine Christianity is so stupid

01:03:11.260 --> 01:03:16.682
that they can’t have women for ordination. Now I am a Woman after all.

01:03:17.729 --> 01:03:23.669
And now as a reaction, women are so angry

01:03:23.869 --> 01:03:26.800
that a girl came to Me the other day, I was in Perth, she said:

01:03:27.000 --> 01:03:29.925
"Mother, why did you call God as ‘He’, why don’t you call as ‘She’?"

01:03:30.125 --> 01:03:36.006
I said: "Because I am ‘She’ that’s why I have to call Him ‘He’."

01:03:37.980 --> 01:03:43.240
But this concept is only still there in the Indian scriptures,

01:03:43.441 --> 01:03:50.401
nowhere, that there’s God
and His Power is Adi Shakti.

01:03:50.602 --> 01:03:56.793
But nowhere, even Islam, in Christianity, in Judaism,

01:03:56.993 --> 01:04:05.252
in what you call, Buddhism, Jainism, nowhere.

01:04:05.858 --> 01:04:09.346
They have not talked of the woman at all.

01:04:09.547 --> 01:04:13.347
As if the whole world is made of men.

01:04:13.547 --> 01:04:17.912
And this is surprisingly for developed countries, in Sweden and countries like this,

01:04:18.113 --> 01:04:22.402
they are talking this nonsense.

01:04:26.754 --> 01:04:31.491
But the solution is only Sahaja Yoga. There’s no other solution.

01:04:31.692 --> 01:04:34.748
Even women go and fight with men, what’s the use?

01:04:34.949 --> 01:04:38.640
Men fight with women, no use. So the best thing for them

01:04:38.841 --> 01:04:42.245
is to get to Sahaja Yoga and understand the value of women.

01:04:42.454 --> 01:04:49.245
They understand what they are for and what is our relationship means, you see.

01:04:49.445 --> 01:04:52.648
It’s such an enjoyment.

01:04:52.848 --> 01:04:56.618
Stupid those people who do not want to have that enjoyment.

01:04:56.819 --> 01:04:59.575
Also your media is responsible, whenever you open the television,

01:04:59.775 --> 01:05:02.473
you just find husband wife fighting, it’s too much.

01:05:02.674 --> 01:05:04.676
All the time fighting, fighting, they show.

01:05:04.877 --> 01:05:08.450
They never show good relationship.

01:05:08.651 --> 01:05:10.680
Once I asked Derek Lee: "Is there any novel

01:05:10.880 --> 01:05:12.910
where they show the romance of husband and wife?’

01:05:13.110 --> 01:05:16.808
He said: "There’s no book". No book in English.

01:05:17.008 --> 01:05:19.974
The whole of English language, there’s no romance of husband and wife,

01:05:20.175 --> 01:05:24.626
can you imagine? I mean that is how you get into tragedies.

01:05:24.826 --> 01:05:31.531
But in India if you see, the literature has certain ethics.

01:05:31.731 --> 01:05:37.442
One of them is only the romance between husband and wife is a romance.

01:05:37.643 --> 01:05:43.432
The rest of it is vulgarity.

01:05:44.837 --> 01:05:49.166
This is the concept.

01:05:50.886 --> 01:05:54.268
Also because mostly they are arranged marriages,

01:05:54.468 --> 01:05:57.850
so they don’t know all this romanticism before marriage.

01:05:58.051 --> 01:06:00.461
So they are waiting for their wife and whole thing,

01:06:00.661 --> 01:06:05.844
and the wife becomes everything to the husband, and same, vice versa.

01:06:06.044 --> 01:06:08.557
So the whole cultural concept has changed.

01:06:08.758 --> 01:06:12.318
It used to be the same way before in every country,

01:06:12.518 --> 01:06:18.051
but now we are advanced you see. In that advancement, we have done this kind of a thing,

01:06:18.252 --> 01:06:25.991
is to make antagonistic societies of men and women.

01:06:26.343 --> 01:06:30.298
It’s very sad. But we are very superficial.

01:06:30.499 --> 01:06:33.622
But the concept itself is wrong.

01:06:33.822 --> 01:06:40.504
I think the basic fundamental thing in the western culture is

01:06:40.704 --> 01:06:43.761
to see and to be seen.

01:06:43.962 --> 01:06:49.206
This is what I’ve realized. That’s the comcept that people should see you

01:06:49.407 --> 01:06:54.383
and you should be able to see others.
I mean, it is so superficial.

01:06:54.584 --> 01:06:57.390
Now they see somebody’s legs and somebody’s knees,

01:06:57.590 --> 01:07:00.746
I mean, what’s the use having a joyless pursuit?

01:07:00.947 --> 01:07:05.931
That person doesn’t belong to you, nothing of
the kind. What’s the use of seeing these things?

01:07:06.131 --> 01:07:12.162
But this, we have become very superficial.

01:07:12.870 --> 01:07:17.926
And it’s going on and on.But I think this will all stop in Sahaja Yoga,

01:07:18.127 --> 01:07:23.307
gradually we’ll start seeing the beauty inside.

01:07:23.508 --> 01:07:28.344
You know Chris Marlow, you know from London.

01:07:28.897 --> 01:07:32.681
He had a wife Jane. She was quite a dry person.

01:07:32.881 --> 01:07:37.599
She herself was saying that: "Mother I am no good for him."

01:07:37.799 --> 01:07:40.252
So they divorced. Then he told Me:

01:07:40.452 --> 01:07:44.254
"Mother I want to marry a girl who has lots of vibrations."

01:07:44.455 --> 01:07:47.042
I said: "What about looks?" "No I don’t see any looks.

01:07:47.243 --> 01:07:52.994
I want to see a girl with vibrations.’
And we had a girl from Amalhabad.

01:07:53.195 --> 01:07:57.283
Very dark, extremely dark and village-like, absolutely.

01:07:57.484 --> 01:07:59.560
You will never, I mean, I don’t think from your standards,

01:07:59.760 --> 01:08:02.853
she may not be beautiful, from My standards, she was very good.

01:08:03.054 --> 01:08:05.343
Full of vibrations. Full of vibrations.

01:08:05.544 --> 01:08:09.318
As soon as she came on the stage, he jumped, said:

01:08:09.519 --> 01:08:14.526
‘This is the one.’ He’s so tall, she’s short and [INAUDIBLE].

01:08:14.727 --> 01:08:17.799
And he looks after her so well, I tell you.

01:08:18.000 --> 01:08:23.058
And then he went to her place, her village, all the way to Amalhabad.

01:08:23.259 --> 01:08:25.279
My sister saw, she said: "What a couple."

01:08:25.480 --> 01:08:30.523
I said: "The couple has chosen each other, I can’t help it."

01:08:30.724 --> 01:08:36.952
He’s so fond of her, he looks after her. She’s very sweet, I mean I really love with that.

01:08:37.153 --> 01:08:42.322
But I didn’t know that this fellow will have the same sort of a feeling.

01:08:43.693 --> 01:08:48.287
Because we are superficial, these things are accepted.

01:08:53.559 --> 01:08:56.436
You should see the inner being.

01:08:56.637 --> 01:09:00.511
How beautiful it is.

01:09:02.211 --> 01:09:07.440
Look at that Elizabeth Taylor, that stupid country of America.

01:09:07.723 --> 01:09:11.781
This was her eighth divorce, I mean eighth honeymoon.

01:09:11.982 --> 01:09:15.303
So they had three thousand or four thousand people

01:09:15.503 --> 01:09:19.315
just standing outside her house to see she is going for her honeymoon.

01:09:19.516 --> 01:09:25.955
Can you imagine stupid? And there were ten helicopters hovering round.

01:09:26.156 --> 01:09:35.200
And they were parachuting and some of them fell on the trees

01:09:35.400 --> 01:09:38.297
and some fell on the people who were there.

01:09:38.498 --> 01:09:41.328
And they were quite excited, very sensational.

01:09:41.529 --> 01:09:45.773
You know, such stupid people these Americans are.

01:09:45.974 --> 01:09:48.562
I don’t know what to say.

01:09:48.763 --> 01:09:51.760
And this lady had divorced eight. And this husband of hers,

01:09:51.960 --> 01:09:55.853
this one, he’s I think, I don’t know how many years younger to her,

01:09:56.053 --> 01:10:00.115
like her son. And also he’s an ordinary man or something.

01:10:00.316 --> 01:10:04.902
But just for the couple.

01:10:05.988 --> 01:10:08.661
She has no sense of marriage, nothing.

01:10:08.862 --> 01:10:11.561
But what she has done is she’s operated her eyelids

01:10:11.761 --> 01:10:18.704
and she’s put her up and all that, and she looks younger now and she says: "I can…"

01:10:21.258 --> 01:10:25.099
There’s no, in that country you cannot mature. So stupid.

01:10:25.300 --> 01:10:31.240
I mean, I was yet to come across people in a group so stupid as that.

01:10:31.441 --> 01:10:34.564
Stupidest people you see. Stupidest.

01:10:34.765 --> 01:10:39.345
You can never mature this way.

01:10:41.548 --> 01:10:46.651
Still Sahaja Yoga is now working. Gregoire feels so exhausted.

01:10:46.852 --> 01:10:50.416
Every time he footsoaks he just lies flat, saying:

01:10:50.616 --> 01:10:55.930
"Mother, please save me from New York.’"It’s terrible.

01:10:57.789 --> 01:11:01.503
There’s no way of maturity.

01:11:01.703 --> 01:11:06.922
They invited Me for this Jungian Society and I went there.

01:11:07.123 --> 01:11:09.586
Of course I didn’t read Jung much but that day I got hold of a book

01:11:09.786 --> 01:11:12.996
and I found out the reason why Jungians have failed.

01:11:13.197 --> 01:11:16.829
So I talked to them they were very much impressed and all that.

01:11:17.030 --> 01:11:20.550
Then the president of that society is eighty years of age,

01:11:20.750 --> 01:11:23.867
and he said that: "Mother I must see You, I have some private thing to talk."

01:11:24.068 --> 01:11:29.925
I said: "All right." This old man came about eighty years of age.

01:11:31.068 --> 01:11:35.228
He said: "I have a very serious problem." I said: "What’s the serious problem."

01:11:35.428 --> 01:11:38.040
He says: "You see I had a keep, because I am a Catholic

01:11:38.240 --> 01:11:41.950
I could not marry the keep but I never told my wife.

01:11:42.151 --> 01:11:47.015
[INAUDIBLE] I never told my wife. So now what am I supposed to do?"

01:11:47.215 --> 01:11:49.866
He said: "Now that my wife is dead and I want that keep

01:11:50.066 --> 01:11:52.564
to stay with Me but she has refused.

01:11:52.765 --> 01:11:57.280
Can you do something to see that the keep stays with Me."

01:11:57.480 --> 01:11:59.687
I said: "It’s all right."

01:11:59.887 --> 01:12:03.616
Eighty year-old man. I was turning sixty by that time.

01:12:03.816 --> 01:12:06.960
An eighty year-old man talking like this to Me.

01:12:07.160 --> 01:12:10.418
I said: "Now what is happening to this man?"

01:12:10.618 --> 01:12:17.251
And he is the chairman of the Jungian Society, International.

01:12:20.641 --> 01:12:25.371
See the maturity of that person. Eighty year-old.

01:12:27.334 --> 01:12:31.316
In America, such cases so much.

01:12:31.517 --> 01:12:33.825
Terrible things.

01:12:34.026 --> 01:12:39.136
Extremely stupid and I don’t know, they have no confidence in themselves.

01:12:39.337 --> 01:12:42.512
All the time they think we should not get old.

01:12:42.713 --> 01:12:46.760
So there was, on the television they showed the cinema actors

01:12:46.960 --> 01:12:50.613
and actresses coming for a dance of "shake",

01:12:50.813 --> 01:12:54.259
and they were all about ninety years of age. Then when they got down

01:12:54.468 --> 01:12:56.737
from the car only, they were shaking. I said: "What’s the use

01:12:56.937 --> 01:13:01.579
of going to shake?" In ninety years, they have not grown.

01:13:01.780 --> 01:13:04.011
Funny dresses they were wearing and all that.

01:13:04.211 --> 01:13:07.670
So when are they going to grow. There’s no maturity.

01:13:07.871 --> 01:13:11.522
The atmosphere is the other way round I think.

01:13:13.053 --> 01:13:17.212
Very stupid.

01:13:24.699 --> 01:13:27.501
Really mad.

01:13:27.701 --> 01:13:31.574
But people start copying them. Whatever they say, people listen to them

01:13:31.775 --> 01:13:34.503
even English I’m surprised. I said that: "You are sensible people.

01:13:34.704 --> 01:13:39.190
Why do you follow these stupid Americans or the French?"

01:13:39.391 --> 01:13:41.760
English people are rather mature. Maybe they lived in India,

01:13:41.961 --> 01:13:44.091
so they have matured quickly I don’t know why.

01:13:44.291 --> 01:13:47.525
But compared with these stupid people they are much more mature.

01:13:47.726 --> 01:13:50.341
And now they are following the American style.

01:13:50.542 --> 01:13:53.436
They used to follow first the French style, now the American style.

01:13:53.636 --> 01:13:58.687
They don’t stand on their own legs.

01:14:00.607 --> 01:14:04.122
But Italians have a good sense of ridicule.

01:14:04.323 --> 01:14:09.385
They understand what is ridiculous, that’s something about them.

01:14:10.790 --> 01:14:15.071
A great sense of ridiculous.

01:14:18.718 --> 01:14:25.345
It will all change in Sahaja Yoga, it will. You are in the Kingdom of God.

01:14:26.006 --> 01:14:28.878
You shouldn’t worry about these things.

01:14:29.079 --> 01:14:31.862
But what to do? If they join us they can come up. But they don’t want to,

01:14:32.063 --> 01:14:36.172
let them be like as they are.

01:14:44.640 --> 01:14:47.874
What else?

01:15:09.047 --> 01:15:13.773
If the lymphatic system is under attack, you may be left-sided.

01:15:16.250 --> 01:15:20.507
You see it is, on the whole, there are only two types of problems,

01:15:20.708 --> 01:15:24.061
actually. Third type doesn’t exist or doesn’t bother us.

01:15:24.261 --> 01:15:27.631
One is the left another is the right, you see.

01:15:27.832 --> 01:15:31.730
Now the lymphatic system is actually the combination of both.

01:15:31.931 --> 01:15:33.995
It’s a psychosomatic disease.

01:15:34.196 --> 01:15:36.878
For that you have to do just three-candle treatment.

01:15:37.079 --> 01:15:40.084
You see it is reduced to such a simple thing,

01:15:40.284 --> 01:15:45.100
either you do three-candle treatment, or you do water treatment.

01:15:45.783 --> 01:15:51.763
The third type is the one where you have been to wrong gurus,

01:15:51.963 --> 01:15:55.394
in the center.

01:15:55.595 --> 01:16:00.683
If you have run some wrong type of meditation, all kinds, that's the third one.

01:16:00.884 --> 01:16:03.972
For that also it’s three-candle treatment, mostly.

01:16:04.173 --> 01:16:07.330
Or maybe little comes there’s a little change also sometimes.

01:16:07.531 --> 01:16:11.288
But whatever it is, this is very simple for physical.

01:16:11.510 --> 01:16:14.431
Anybody has lymphatic system problem has to do

01:16:14.632 --> 01:16:18.049
left side treatment first. So this is psychosomatic.

01:16:18.250 --> 01:16:21.909
First you must get rid of the psycho side, so do the left side.

01:16:22.110 --> 01:16:26.891
When it is cleared out, then right side is not difficult.

01:16:27.092 --> 01:16:31.065
If you are too right-sided, then what happens?

01:16:31.265 --> 01:16:34.775
Like a pendulum, you move from right to left.

01:16:34.976 --> 01:16:37.221
Then psychosomatic troubles start.

01:16:37.421 --> 01:16:43.587
The best is first to remove the left, then is look after the right.

01:16:43.788 --> 01:16:48.857
Sahaja Yoga is a very simple way of clearing. It works.

01:16:49.058 --> 01:16:52.275
Somebody should help you in left side is to give you

01:16:52.475 --> 01:16:56.084
bandhan on your chakras with a candle.

01:16:56.285 --> 01:17:00.438
Put a candle on one side of the Left Swadisthana

01:17:00.638 --> 01:17:05.418
and also one before the photograph.

01:17:09.612 --> 01:17:12.081
Because it’s all due to viruses.

01:17:12.281 --> 01:17:15.247
And the viruses are there because your attention in the left.

01:17:15.448 --> 01:17:19.668
Once your attention goes away from there, you are rid of that.

01:17:19.869 --> 01:17:22.566
All right?

01:17:22.767 --> 01:17:26.769
It’s not complicated. Sahaja Yoga is very simple.

01:17:26.970 --> 01:17:32.835
You know we have cured people who were about to go on the dialysis.

01:17:33.036 --> 01:17:35.445
Kidney has been cured. Can you imagine?

01:17:35.646 --> 01:17:38.710
Of course people with blood cancer that has been cured, no doubt.

01:17:38.911 --> 01:17:44.393
But imagine the kidney, people were going on the dialysis.

01:17:58.802 --> 01:18:03.098
Of course. I mean, we make the human beings.

01:18:03.631 --> 01:18:07.681
You first, if you are evolving,

01:18:07.881 --> 01:18:11.484
you are also evolving human beings with you.

01:18:11.685 --> 01:18:16.302
So it’s for the emancipation of the whole world.

01:18:19.928 --> 01:18:24.342
It’s not only your evolution. No, no, not at all. That was over.

01:18:24.543 --> 01:18:30.218
Now I have told about that in [INAUDIBLE], is that,

01:18:30.418 --> 01:18:35.349
from Buddha’s future they say there will be a future Buddha

01:18:35.550 --> 01:18:39.575
who will be Maitreya. Maitreya means Three Mothers together,

01:18:39.776 --> 01:18:45.307
will be the future Buddha. And that is called as Bodhisattva.

01:18:45.508 --> 01:18:49.261
Now the Bodhisattva is the One who will become Buddha,

01:18:49.462 --> 01:18:56.660
means who will get enlightened and will work for the other people.

01:18:56.861 --> 01:18:59.640
So is already described, and you don’t have to suffer,

01:18:59.840 --> 01:19:02.607
you don’t have to do anything as it was before individually,

01:19:02.808 --> 01:19:07.208
but now you’ll work with the collective.

01:19:07.409 --> 01:19:10.876
So, you have to work with the collective otherwise you have no meaning.

01:19:11.077 --> 01:19:14.038
Also you cannot be cleansed unless and until you come to collective.

01:19:14.239 --> 01:19:16.531
If you say: "I’m staying at home and I’m doing all the puja

01:19:16.731 --> 01:19:20.108
and all that", doesn’t work out.

01:19:20.309 --> 01:19:25.231
Like a nail if it is cut, it doesn’t grow.

01:19:29.675 --> 01:19:32.840
Very simple.

01:19:38.860 --> 01:19:43.171
It’s not for one person no doubt. I mean how can it be, for one.

01:19:43.371 --> 01:19:45.881
Because the time has come for doing collective work now.

01:19:46.082 --> 01:19:50.398
The whole world has to change.

01:19:54.741 --> 01:19:58.382
Yogi: Shri Mother, will we ever be able to go to Tasmania?

01:20:15.048 --> 01:20:19.087
Yes, Tasmania, they have to come. They have to come here.

01:20:19.288 --> 01:20:23.231
Like you see, Sicily, we are now having lots of Sahaja Yogis there.

01:20:23.432 --> 01:20:25.961
They all came down. Then I can now go to Sicily.

01:20:26.161 --> 01:20:29.471
We have very few people in Tasmania.

01:20:29.671 --> 01:20:31.771
Now that’s the point.

01:20:31.971 --> 01:20:36.844
So when they will come and they’ll get their Realization then I can go.

01:20:37.045 --> 01:20:44.054
You see, if I go to a place it is like,

01:20:44.254 --> 01:20:49.019
should I say, the seeds being sprouted and nobody to look after.

01:20:49.220 --> 01:20:54.259
Yogi: There were quite a number of people who came from Tasmania.

01:20:55.868 --> 01:20:58.043
Shri Mataji: They should come, they should.

01:20:58.243 --> 01:21:01.497
They should go with their bandhans and try to save their country.

01:21:01.697 --> 01:21:06.129
Yes, they should. If they go and establish it, I’ll definitely go.

01:21:06.329 --> 01:21:10.013
It’s quite a remarkable place that Tasmania is.

01:21:10.214 --> 01:21:19.845
Talisman means, talisman all the secret, magic.

01:21:20.046 --> 01:21:24.266
It is talisman, from that Tasmania word must have come.

01:21:25.102 --> 01:21:29.000
Yogi: How many Tasmanians are there here?

01:21:31.601 --> 01:21:36.485
Shri Mataji: Still very few to fight those negativities there.

01:21:36.686 --> 01:21:41.631
Very negative. Very negative, isn’t it?

01:21:43.168 --> 01:21:48.146
Just like, we have Calcutta.

01:21:48.347 --> 01:21:50.547
Too much of black magic. Too much.

01:21:50.748 --> 01:21:56.693
But gradually we have now got it out. It’s changed.

01:21:56.894 --> 01:22:01.585
One side is they are all full of black magic, those who believe in God.

01:22:01.786 --> 01:22:06.306
The another side are communists. But still now we have thousands.

01:22:06.507 --> 01:22:12.195
It is remarkable. But people had to work very hard for it, very hard.

01:22:15.361 --> 01:22:23.861
So many people went from Nagpur, from Mumbai, from Delhi to help them.

01:22:25.280 --> 01:22:30.471
Still some places I’ve not been, like Ceylon, Assam.

01:22:30.671 --> 01:22:33.746
We have some coming from there.

01:22:33.947 --> 01:22:38.100
I told them next year I’ll try to be there.

01:22:54.021 --> 01:22:59.169
Hands like that? You want to know what’s the symbol?

01:23:00.961 --> 01:23:03.892
This is for assurance.

01:23:04.093 --> 01:23:07.619
See? This is for assurance. It has powers.

01:23:07.820 --> 01:23:13.104
This hand has tremendous powers. And this one is for giving.

01:23:13.305 --> 01:23:16.671
You see? So these are two aspects.

01:23:16.871 --> 01:23:22.958
But actually as you know this is the power of action.

01:23:23.158 --> 01:23:27.054
So it acts. And this is the power of desire.

01:23:27.255 --> 01:23:30.628
So this is the Love that’s flowing of your Mother,

01:23:30.828 --> 01:23:35.539
and this is how She is active.

01:23:36.297 --> 01:23:39.363
But now I have given up. I used to do it in the beginning it was needed,

01:23:39.563 --> 01:23:44.842
now it’s not necessary. It works even without that.

